{"thag2.42:0.1":"Theragatha 2.42 ","thag2.42:0.2":"Dukanipata ","thag2.42:0.3":"Pancamavagga ","thag2.42:0.4":"Dhammapalattheragatha ","thag2.42:1.1":"“Yo have daharo bhikkhu, ","thag2.42:1.2":"yunjati buddhasasane; ","thag2.42:1.3":"Jagaro sa hi suttesu, ","thag2.42:1.4":"amogham tassa jivitam. ","thag2.42:2.1":"Tasma saddhanca silanca, ","thag2.42:2.2":"pasadam dhammadassanam; ","thag2.42:2.3":"Anuyunjetha medhavi, ","thag2.42:2.4":"saram buddhana sasanan”ti. ","thag2.42:2.5":"… Dhammapalo thero …. "}